Interface Handler

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    EventListener, Processor, Writer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractEventListener, AbstractProcessor, AbstractStreamWriter, AbstractWriter, AbstractXmiStreamWriter, CountingEventListener, DefaultMapperWriter, EcoreMapper, IndentingXmiStreamWriter, LoggingEventListener, NoopProcessor, ProgressEventListener, TimerEventListener, XmiStreamWriter, XPathResolver

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public interface Handler
    A object that handles events received from a Notifier.
